Cadence
=======

Cadence is a rhythm manager.  See
http://rescrv.net/w/2023/04/04/detecting-mania/ for more information.

Included are two implementations.

rust:  This version is single-user command-line.  Mostly complete.  Supports
smoothing and deferring.  Bugs are tagged with TODO.

python:  Multi-user version meant to be embedded in a web app.  Does not
support smoothing, but does support deferring better.  Fewer bugs.
